sentence: In early trading on Wednesday, shares of Goldman Sachs Group ( GS ) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.8%.
Year to date, Goldman Sachs Group has lost about 10.2% of its value.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Procter & Gamble ( PG ), trading down 0.0%.
Procter & Gamble is lower by about 1.5% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are AT&T ( T ), trading flat on the day, and JPMorgan Chase & Co. ( JPM ), trading up 1.6% on the day.
